HEADWORD: Provençal
<hw>Pro`ven`⟦cced⟧al"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A native or inhabitant of Provence in France.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The Provencal language. See <er>Langue
